{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-blog-blog-details-js","path":"/blog/qa-evolution-from-manual-to-ai/","result":{"data":{"bloggerPost":{"slug":"qa-evolution-from-manual-to-ai","id":"66c57bd6-9a88-52b4-9974-2c31d57e351f","title":"QA Evolution: From Manual to AI","content":"<p>&nbsp;</p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgHjFqwoo-o2rvgV31EzIBD952xlVqn33mZh7EefKPOi6QYkkIOI-ArkMQJQUZ8ChvIZfo1a3txK4812rkx-zm3VaNGUSqK7ZfuezjoUi59Q51AyYlIfMBKEge3Yhccl3ellUxMpEhwoPbuL3ehbiOYy0bugELIVXcK0c3Vby2HhgleD_O7hVcfkEsd\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"720\" data-original-width=\"1279\" height=\"294\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgHjFqwoo-o2rvgV31EzIBD952xlVqn33mZh7EefKPOi6QYkkIOI-ArkMQJQUZ8ChvIZfo1a3txK4812rkx-zm3VaNGUSqK7ZfuezjoUi59Q51AyYlIfMBKEge3Yhccl3ellUxMpEhwoPbuL3ehbiOYy0bugELIVXcK0c3Vby2HhgleD_O7hVcfkEsd=w445-h294\" width=\"445\" /></a></div><br /><br /><br /><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;\">🚀The Fast-Moving World of Software</span></p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1132\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">Imagine you are building a high-speed car. In the beginning, you check every bolt by hand. It’s slow, - but you know that car inside out. The world starts moving faster. People don't want one car a month; They want a thousand cars a day.</p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1133\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">This is the story of how our QA (Quality Assurance) team stopped being just \"checkers\" and started becoming<span class=\"white-space-pre\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"> </span><span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">architects of intelligence</span></p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1134\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">🔍The Craftsperson's Touch:</span></p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1135\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">Every great story has a beginning. Ours was<span class=\"white-space-pre\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"> </span><span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Manual Testing</span>. We were the first line of defense. We navigated every screen and clicked every button. It was personal. Thorough. Responsible. But as the software world shifted into \"Fast-Forward\" mode, we realized we couldn't just work harder; we had to work smarter</p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1136\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">⚙️Forging the Automation Power Suit</span></p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1137\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">We didn't throw away our manual skills; we gave them a \"<span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">power suit.</span>\" We started Automation. We wrote scripts to handle the repetitive, boring stuff so we could focus on the complex puzzles. But even then, there was a catch: Automation scripts execute exactly what they are programmed to do — nothing more, nothing less.</p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1138\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">💡<span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">The AI Ignition: When Thought Took Flight</span></p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1139\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">The real \"Lightbulb Moment\" happened when we started researching Artificial Intelligence. We didn't want to just automate<span class=\"white-space-pre\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"> </span><span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><em style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">actions</em></span>; we wanted to automate<span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span class=\"white-space-pre\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"> </span></span><span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><em style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">thought</em></span>. We started small with Automatic Cucumber Generation.</p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1140\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span class=\"white-space-pre\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"> </span>Instead of humans spending hours writing out test scenarios in plain language (Gherkin), we taught an AI to read the requirements and write the scenarios for us. It was like having a co-writer who never gets tired and never misses a detail.</p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1141\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">🤖<span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Our Intelligent Partner: The Evolution of the QA Mind</span></p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1142\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">Once we saw what AI could do with words,</p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1143\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span class=\"white-space-pre\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"> </span>we asked: \"<span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Can it think like a tester?</span>\"<span class=\"white-space-pre\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"> </span></p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1144\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">That's where we are today. We aren't just using AI tools; we are building a QA Agent. Think of this agent as a digital teammate. It doesn't just follow a script; it explores the application, finds bugs we didn't think to look for, and learns from every click.</p><hr class=\"reader-divider-block__horizontal-rule\" style=\"background-color: white; border-bottom-style: initial; border-color: rgba(140, 140, 140, 0.2) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); border-image: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-top-style: solid; border-width: 0.888889px 0px 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; height: 1px; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; width: 584px;\" /><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1145\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">🧠<span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Building an Autonomous QA Agent</span></p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1146\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">Our system uses multiple specialized AI agents coordinated by a central Orchestrator Agent. The<span class=\"white-space-pre\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"> </span><span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Orchestrator Agent</span><span class=\"white-space-pre\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"> </span>acts as the control layer of the platform. It manages execution flow, maintains context, and dynamically activates different agents during the testing process.</p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1147\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">The testing workflow begins when a user provides:<span class=\"white-space-pre\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"> </span><span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">A target application URL</span></p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1148\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">The orchestrator initializes a testing session and determines which agents should be activated.</p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1149\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">🧩 Agent Workflow</span></p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1150\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">The system operates through a sequence of specialized agents:&nbsp;</p><img alt=\"Article content\" class=\"ivm-view-attr__img--centered reader-image-block__img evi-image lazy-image ember-view\" height=\"278\" id=\"ember1151\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5612AQFxSU-ji7CYYw/article-inline_image-shrink_1000_1488/B56ZyuM51VHsAQ-/0/1772449150380?e=1773878400&amp;v=beta&amp;t=BuxVWH1ODdTXoFzizoPWAIuCBhf5bzyJHfgRewJ8Y9w\" style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position: 50% center; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: cover; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); display: block; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; height: auto; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center center; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 632px;\" width=\"632\" /><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1150\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1152\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">Each agent performs a specific task while sharing the same execution context. The Orchestrator continuously monitors system state, determines the next action, and ensures the workflow progresses logically. This allows the system to behave like a single intelligent QA engineer exploring the application, rather than a set of disconnected automation scripts.</p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1153\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">🌍<span class=\"white-space-pre\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"> </span><span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Toward Autonomous Testing</span></p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1154\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">This architecture represents a shift from:</p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1155\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; outline: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9) none 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Script-Based Testing → Autonomous, Intent-Driven Testing</span></p><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1156\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; pointer-events: all; vertical-align: baseline;\">Instead of defining every step manually, the system dynamically understands the application, plans tests, executes them, and learns from each run.This is not about replacing testers — it is about empowering QA teams with intelligent systems that scale with modern software development</p><hr class=\"reader-divider-block__horizontal-rule\" style=\"background-color: white; border-bottom-style: initial; border-color: rgba(140, 140, 140, 0.2) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); border-image: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-top-style: solid; border-width: 0.888889px 0px 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, Ubuntu, Oxygen, &quot;Oxygen Sans&quot;, Cantarell, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; height: 1px; margin: 0px 0px 32px; padding: 0px; width: 584px;\" /><p class=\"ember-view reader-text-block__paragraph\" id=\"ember1157\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-style: none; border-width: 